alakkai (அளக்கை)
=========

* A tool to create surveys, let people vote and see the results. The name alakkai is the Tamil term (அளக்கை) for survey
* For a screencast of version 1 of this software, see: <URL Should come here #TODO >
* To get alakkai working:
1) Install golang from http://golang.org
2) Install mongodb from http://www.mongodb.org/downloads
3) From your terminal: git clone git://github.com/psankar/alakkai.git
4) Edit alakkai.go and change the various CONFIG_* variables to suit your need.
5) go build alakkai.go ;#Ensure that everything builds fine
6) mongod ;#Starting mongodb server
7) ./alakkai ;#Starting alakkai server
8) In your browser, visit http://<server>:<port>/create for creating surveys. The <server> and <port> were the ones that you configured in step 4


