Programming
=============

* The program is written using the go programming language for the server-side software development. Javascript and HTML are used for the web front end.
* mongodb is used for storing the surveys and the responses, serving as the backend.
* If you are sending any code or string translations or any type of contributions to be merged with the alakkai project, it will be released in the same Creative Commons Zero License as alakkai. Send your contributions only if you agree to freely distribute your changes as mentioned by the license. 
* You can search for TODO or FIXME to know various open issues.


